2. Type in the search bar ‚Äî verify the Posts/People toggle appears
3. Switch to "People" tab, type a name or username ‚Äî verify user suggestions dropdown shows matching users
4. Press Enter ‚Äî verify full user search results render as cards with avatar, name, @username, badge
5. Click a user card ‚Äî verify it navigates to the correct profile page
